341937460#1 - 點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1645636627fc4e23bc498c429a80fba3f7c87fd4","tid":2214430,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"30c7068d10018b41841bd100e14f9c375cf1205e","tid":2214430,"uid":241151,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"網上有記載以前左膠有咩人，當然，宜家更多：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uRnG8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uRnG8i.jpg&h=d11ba60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hK7Ka1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhK7Ka1F.jpg&h=cd3b3a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNhmXGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNhmXGG.jpg&h=a97b59a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ME4Xv1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna